    "Similarly, Romero et al. [50] and May et al.",
    "[51] designed HDTs in the industrial domain to utilize physical, sensory, cognitive performance, anthropometric data, functional capabilities, knowledge, skills, and expertise.",
    "Moreover, kinematic data collected by sensors play a crucial role in industrial production, and studies by Bilberg et al. [52], Peruzzini et al.",
    "[53], Shen et al. [54], and Greco et al.",
    "[22] showcased the use of sensors to monitor human motion, evaluate workload severity, and assess muscle fatigue."
